{"tid":1787967,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"欲罷不能 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-12-18T09:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T09:55:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8742c352e8b411bb4e865eb06da0d887a6f4d4f0","tid":1787967,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191218/20826868/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F20826868%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Bui8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=4fa3237c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F20826868%2F&h=a9225067\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191218/20826868/</a><br />\n<br />\n欲罷不能 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191218/large/1576574001_f068.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576574001_f068.jpg&h=7008d52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十二月六日，英國《金融時報》報道，香港偽律政司長鄭若驊上月在倫敦街頭，遭香港僑民包圍聲討，失足倒地，其後一度堅拒回港，請求辭職，只是中共不准，還押解她到北京「療傷」。律政司循例否認，但鄭若驊十一月十四日輕輕一跌，竟然到十二月三日才返港，「養傷」之久，實堪玩味。<br />\n<br />\n而據路透社九月初公布的錄音，偽行政長官鄭月娥曾語香港一些大商家：「如可選擇，我會辭職。」鄭月娥也循例否認曾求引退，但身為長官，觸發激烈民變，連辭呈都不必向中共遞上，聽候發落，恐怕不會有人相信。<br />\n<br />\n在文明社會，官員執意辭職，斷無辭不得之理。孔子說：「大臣者，以道事君，不可則止。」民國四年，梁啟超就因不滿袁世凱大總統陰謀做皇帝，辭去幣制局總裁職務，袁世凱也無可奈何。當然，黑社會則和文明社會不同：「一日黑社會，一世黑社會。」澳洲墨爾本二零一四年七月就傳出一段小新聞：兩名彪身惡漢突然闖入一修車廠，對一名工人拳腳交加，打個半死，然後逃去，被打者原來曾加入黑幫，未獲准而退出，於是舊日的同夥前來執行幫規。那兩個惡漢後來被捕，一個叫邁耶（Vincent Meyer），一個叫舍瓦尼（Hawre Sherwani）。<br />\n<br />\n然則二鄭連辭職自由都沒有，並不奇怪。誰叫她們當初貪慕權力與金錢。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"137efa6163e5117b24d36580d0da316dfb32455f","tid":1787967,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}